    {
      "id": "1b66f57e-679b-4086-be5e-d4ee4a1f5255",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient ${\\cal E} : \\frac {x^2}{4a^2} + \\frac {y^2}{4b^2} = 1$,\net ${\\cal E}' : \\frac {x^2}{a^2} + \\frac {y^2}{b^2} = 1$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal E} : \\frac {x^2}{4a^2} + \\frac {y^2}{4b^2} = 1\\)</span>, et <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal E}&#39; : \\frac {x^2}{a^2} + \\frac {y^2}{b^2} = 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "936ad0ab-6dc1-4bc6-a55a-d068fb49f363",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "CNS sur $u,v,w$ pour que la droite d'équation $ux+vy+w=0$ soit\n    tangente à ${\\cal E}'$ ?",
        "html": "<p>CNS sur <span class=\"math inline\">\\(u,v,w\\)</span> pour que la droite d’équation <span class=\"math inline\">\\(ux+vy+w=0\\)</span> soit tangente à <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal E}&#39;\\)</span> ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "03cf07e8-bbe4-403e-8a11-59a9fc127695",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$a^2u^2+b^2v^2 -w^2=0$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(a^2u^2+b^2v^2 -w^2=0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "41ab68d1-b4e8-4c70-838c-76fc37a57b5e",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $(MP)$, $(MQ)$ deux tangentes à ${\\cal E}'$ avec $M,P,Q \\in {\\cal E}$.\n    Montrer que $(PQ)$ est aussi tangente à ${\\cal E}$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\((MP)\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\((MQ)\\)</span> deux tangentes à <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal E}&#39;\\)</span> avec <span class=\"math inline\">\\(M,P,Q \\in {\\cal E}\\)</span>. Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\((PQ)\\)</span> est aussi tangente à <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal E}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e66d05fb-b217-4128-af70-253d33b4923b",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$M : \\begin{pmatrix}2a\\cos\\theta\\cr2a\\sin\\theta\\end{pmatrix}$,\n             $P : \\begin{pmatrix}2a\\cos\\alpha\\cr2a\\sin\\alpha\\end{pmatrix}$ :\n             $(MP)$ est tangente à ${\\cal E}'\n             \\Leftrightarrow \\theta \\equiv \\alpha \\pm \\frac{2\\pi}3\\ [2\\pi]$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(M : \\begin{pmatrix}2a\\cos\\theta\\cr2a\\sin\\theta\\end{pmatrix}\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P : \\begin{pmatrix}2a\\cos\\alpha\\cr2a\\sin\\alpha\\end{pmatrix}\\)</span> : <span class=\"math inline\">\\((MP)\\)</span> est tangente à <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal E}&#39;\n             \\Leftrightarrow \\theta \\equiv \\alpha \\pm \\frac{2\\pi}3\\ [2\\pi]\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
